help.description: Returns a quick help guide for CRBT.

HELP_DESCRIPTION:
Type {prefix} in the chat and click {botIcon} tco get a list of Slash Commands.
You can also right click or long press a message or a user for quick actions.

CRBT comes with handy and powerful features, such as creating reminders ({reminder}), announcing new and leaving members ({settings}), getting Discord and web info ({infoCommands}, etc.)...

...with more to come! Stay up to date on CRBT by joining [our server]({link}).

settings.description: Configurați setările CRBT pe acest server.

SETTINGS_DESCRIPTION: Utilizați meniul de mai jos pentru a actualiza setările acestui server.
SETTINGS_COLOR_DESCRIPTION:
Customize your Polls, Giveaways and more by setting a theme! Auto Theming lets CRBT always take the primary color from the server's icon, or you can pick a color manually using a HEX code or one of the presets.

It is currently set to **{color}**.
